{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"36":"Tribulations"},"section_detail":{"36":{"hadithnumber_first":3927,"hadithnumber_last":4099,"arabicnumber_first":3927,"arabicnumber_last":4099}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3946,"arabicnumber":3946,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن بشار، حدثنا روح بن عبادة، حدثنا اشعث، عن الحسن، عن سمرة بن جندب، عن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم قال \" من صلى الصبح فهو في ذمة الله عز وجل","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":36,"hadith":21}}]}